Cisco Security Advisory: Cisco 11500 Content Services Switch SSL
Malformed Client Certificate Vulnerability
==========================================================================

Document ID: 67919

Revision 1.0

For Public Release 2005 October 19 1600 UTC (GMT)
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------

